  "title": "Five round blinking red UFOs spotted moving in circles in Londrina [2000]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/five-round-blinking-red-ufos-spotted-moving-in-circles-in-londrina-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-s5",
  "content": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>OCT 22nd, 2000</strong>. Time: 16h15pm. Duration: 3 seconds. Five (5) unidentified flying objects were spotted moving in circles at a very high altitude downtown Londrina, State of Paraná. The five round blinking red UFOs had the aspect of a star and were very close to each other in their trajectory, going from East to West at varying speed. Three witnesses who observed the sighting live in the city center and saw the unknown objects with the naked eye and under good visibility conditions. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.583. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni na cidade de Londrina, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>OCT 22nd, 2000. Time: 16h15pm. Duration: 3 seconds. Five (5) unidentified flying objects were spotted moving in circles at a very high altitude downtown Londrina, State of Paraná. The five round blinking red UFOs had the aspect of a star and were very close to each other in their trajectory, going from East to West [&hellip;]</p>\n",
